    <template>
     A cloud engineer helps companies use online cloud services to store, manage, and run their data and applications.
     They set up and take care of cloud platforms like AWS, Microsoft Azure, or Google Cloud so everything works smoothly and safely.
     Cloud engineers make sure the systems are secure, reliable, and can grow as the company needs.
